  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ivan returns to his village after five years and faces new challenges.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Russian Village Simulator 2</strong> is a game that allows the player to immerse himself in the atmosphere of life in a real Russian village. The game features various activities that are characteristic of life in the village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/f3ed792dbc50c91a7842bc030eda3c07.poster.avif?t=1750866571\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/f3ed792dbc50c91a7842bc030eda3c07.webm?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/f3ed792dbc50c91a7842bc030eda3c07.mp4?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game you can garden, grow various fruits and vegetables, plant your own garden, take care of animals and breed them, harvest. You can also fish on the lake, hunt wild animals, collect berries and mushrooms in the forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/60a2cc92c73b49a0e02d8362e7494131.poster.avif?t=1750866571\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/60a2cc92c73b49a0e02d8362e7494131.webm?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/60a2cc92c73b49a0e02d8362e7494131.mp4?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village has its own bathhouse, which you need to build, and then wash and rest after hard work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also do crafts, create various products from wood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/942437fb4e4ded68c120156dbeb124c6.poster.avif?t=1750866571\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/942437fb4e4ded68c120156dbeb124c6.webm?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/942437fb4e4ded68c120156dbeb124c6.mp4?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An important aspect of the game is communication with other villagers. The player can help them in difficult situations, exchange resources and participate in the social life of the village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/969e51fcc7e9c4565c0fec55b38d3d40.poster.avif?t=1750866571\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/969e51fcc7e9c4565c0fec55b38d3d40.webm?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/969e51fcc7e9c4565c0fec55b38d3d40.mp4?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also has elements of economic strategy. The player can sell his goods, develop his farm and improve his dwelling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Russian Village Simulator 2</strong> is a game that allows the player to immerse himself in the atmosphere of life in a real Russian village and enjoy its simplicity and beauty.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ivan returns to his village after five years and faces new challenges.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Russian Village Simulator 2</strong> is a game that allows the player to immerse himself in the atmosphere of life in a real Russian village. The game features various activities that are characteristic of life in the village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/f3ed792dbc50c91a7842bc030eda3c07.poster.avif?t=1750866571\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/f3ed792dbc50c91a7842bc030eda3c07.webm?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/f3ed792dbc50c91a7842bc030eda3c07.mp4?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game you can garden, grow various fruits and vegetables, plant your own garden, take care of animals and breed them, harvest. You can also fish on the lake, hunt wild animals, collect berries and mushrooms in the forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/60a2cc92c73b49a0e02d8362e7494131.poster.avif?t=1750866571\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/60a2cc92c73b49a0e02d8362e7494131.webm?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/60a2cc92c73b49a0e02d8362e7494131.mp4?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village has its own bathhouse, which you need to build, and then wash and rest after hard work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also do crafts, create various products from wood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/942437fb4e4ded68c120156dbeb124c6.poster.avif?t=1750866571\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/942437fb4e4ded68c120156dbeb124c6.webm?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/942437fb4e4ded68c120156dbeb124c6.mp4?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An important aspect of the game is communication with other villagers. The player can help them in difficult situations, exchange resources and participate in the social life of the village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/969e51fcc7e9c4565c0fec55b38d3d40.poster.avif?t=1750866571\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/969e51fcc7e9c4565c0fec55b38d3d40.webm?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3714790/extras/969e51fcc7e9c4565c0fec55b38d3d40.mp4?t=1750866571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also has elements of economic strategy. The player can sell his goods, develop his farm and improve his dwelling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Russian Village Simulator 2</strong> is a game that allows the player to immerse himself in the atmosphere of life in a real Russian village and enjoy its simplicity and beauty.</p>",
